      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      (package private) void directionRBSelected(javafx.event.ActionEvent event)
      Handles the event in which a RadioButton with a direction is selected.
      (package private) void fillSquare(javafx.event.ActionEvent event)
      This method generates an instance of MagicSquare and one of GridPane with the MagicSquare's recently created instance's data, then fills the labelMatrix with each corresponding value from the matrix from the recently generated MagicSquare, assigns the value of the MagicConstant to the last row and column of the label matrix and finally sets the GridPane as the content for the ScrollPane.
      (package private) void highlight(Controller.MyLabel l)
      This method searches for each MyLabel object contained within labelMatrix that has its column and row id equals as the MyLabel that has been clicked, and then changes its textFill attribute to Color.RED while setting every other label's to Color.BLACK
      (package private) void initPosChanged(javafx.event.ActionEvent event)
      A listener method designed to change the text and values of each RadioButton used in this program.
      (package private) void showSquare()
      This method gets the data of the magic square located in ms and displays its content in MyLabel s contained within a GridPane, representing the magic square.

        void fillSquare(javafx.event.ActionEvent event)
